{"tid":1305930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非路綫思想武裝［說好的「理」性呢？］打不還手係助紂為虐","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T08:14:18.000Z","uid":149630,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b65137822c938700e27b9b16102434a4a53ba6df","tid":1305930,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:38:54.000Z","msg":"果位義士感性上我好敬佩<br />\n但冷酷嘅政治思考<br />\n話畀我知後果不堪設想<br />\n<br />\n義士畀人打到企唔到跌倒<br />\n其實已經係腦震盪<br />\n如果再起身捱打<br />\n係置自己安危於不顧<br />\n雖然話「我驚乜撚，我使乜走」<br />\n而且警已報<br />\n但大家心知警方幫邊邊<br />\n打不還手，只贏得自我嘅道德榮耀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">極端嘅任人魚肉，只會助長更多暴力上門</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>睇片見到藍絲明顯係愈打愈興起愈爽<br />\n愈打愈想打</strong></span></span><br />\n亦係其他藍絲面前做左示範<br />\n原來佢地任打唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果義士就算唔還手<br />\n哪怕擺起防禦姿勢<br />\n藍絲每次進攻都要等時機<br />\n成本亦增加<br />\n甚至擔心義士還擊<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">義士打不還手，<br />\n係和理非路線上<br />\n或造成强大而過火嘅道德典範</span></span><br />\n之後嘅和理非派系如果受到攻擊<br />\n如果還擊，係咪就失去左道德高地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">令之後嘅抗爭者連以武力制止進一步嘅暴力<br />\n都抵受住呢個道德典範而來嘅道德壓力<br />\n<br />\n任人宰割，恐非和理非應走之路<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">暴力無理性基礎，無限制<br />\n武力具理性基礎，而克制</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">以武制暴，令使用暴力成本增加<br />\n令佢唔會隨便打人，打完都唔會立刻追擊<br />\n以防還擊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算唔想還手，都唔好任人打<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">唔還擊都要走！</span></span><br />\n每個義士嘅生命都比藍絲可貴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gr26X7B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgr26X7B.png&h=a87dd713&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed211fc7c1a07993795bd35fbc976b3bdf16695b","tid":1305930,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:39:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9304d915bfb3e253d6c1d775dc33b3149297d0ae","tid":1305930,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17778eeb2176165dd22605d8f76443bdbc7fec8a","tid":1305930,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd84480e03c657851b2c0a75525b747abfc46aec","tid":1305930,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7a0dee04466da17c04b7c5c26d48838f2842acf","tid":1305930,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:43:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f76bd69941fb3f5e729ffdf97d310b20128461a4","tid":1305930,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:46:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26409a6808bd2fabae09a5785ece55cf4c4cc2af","tid":1305930,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:46:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70a6def4a8b88eb8a08b9314b15d36edd577e86e","tid":1305930,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:46:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7dc10ae50d0b693401a8c5eb88cb731bb2cf373b","tid":1305930,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:47:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78b928e8ec0ddbcd04657a7a07599ffe8cc36535","tid":1305930,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:47:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21027f4ef8f8009089ffc37ada078ee2294aa716","tid":1305930,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:48:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3660d63067281ab61c388eda8